<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="all-pron">all <strong><em>pron</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ɔːl/    美 /ɔːl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>全部；全体：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All for one, one for all. 
人人为我，我为人人。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All of them enjoyed themselves. 
他们都玩得很愉快。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>唯一；一切：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All (that) I need is peace and quiet. 
我需要的是安宁与平静。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All is not gold that glitters. 
闪光的未必都是金子。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="all-in-all">all in all</h3>
<p>1.<strong>总而言之 (altogether)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All in all her mother and I are very happy with her progress.
总而言之，看到她的进步我和她妈妈都很高兴。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 1</footer></div>

<h3 id="in-all">in all</h3>
<p>1.<strong>总共 (altogether)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How many people were there in all at the party? 
出席聚会的共有多少人？</p></div>

<h3 id="not-at-all">not ... at all</h3>
<p>1.<strong>根本不；一点也不：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The ﬁlm was not interesting at all.
电影一点儿也没意思。</p></div>

<h3 id="not-at-all_1">not at all</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[客套语] 不客气：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— It’s so kind of you and your parents. 
非常感谢您和您的父母。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Not at all. 
不客气。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>All<strong><em>_</em></strong>_ is important is that you are doing your best and moving in the right direction.  （2010 浙江改）  </li>
<li>— Do you mind if I record your lecture? alongside
— <strong><em>_</em></strong>_(一点儿也不). Go ahead.  （2008 江 苏改）  </li>
<li>That’s an unpleasant thing to say about your father after <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ he’s done for you.<br />
A.something<br />
B.anything<br />
C.all<br />
D.that  </li>
<li>All we need <strong><em>_</em></strong> (be) a small piece of land where we can plant various kinds of fruit trees throughout the growing seasons of the year.  （2014 湖南改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. that  2. Not at all  3. C  4. is  </p></div>